<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Accountability System</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: transparent;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .accountability-container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .accountability-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 25px;
        }

        /* First row: 3 cards */
        .stage-card:nth-child(1) {
            grid-column: 1;
        }

        .stage-card:nth-child(2) {
            grid-column: 2;
        }

        .stage-card:nth-child(3) {
            grid-column: 3;
        }

        /* Second row: 1 card + recovery spanning 2 columns */
        .stage-card:nth-child(4) {
            grid-column: 1;
        }

        .recovery-section {
            grid-column: 2 / 4; /* Spans columns 2 and 3 */
        }

        .stage-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 35px 28px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .stage-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 5px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .stage-card.safe::before {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #10B981 0%, #059669 100%);
        }

        .stage-card.warning::before {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F59E0B 0%, #D97706 100%);
        }

        .stage-card.cooldown::before {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F97316 0%, #EA580C 100%);
        }

        .stage-card.danger::before {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #EF4444 0%, #DC2626 100%);
        }

        .stage-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .stage-card.safe:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
        }

        .stage-card.warning:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.3);
        }

        .stage-card.cooldown:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.3);
        }

        .stage-card.danger:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        }

        .stage-icon {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .safe .stage-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2) 0%, rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1) 100%);
        }

        .warning .stage-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2) 0%, rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1) 100%);
        }

        .cooldown .stage-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2) 0%, rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.1) 100%);
        }

        .danger .stage-icon {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.2) 0%, rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.1) 100%);
        }

        .stage-card:hover .stage-icon {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
        }

        .stage-number {
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            opacity: 0.6;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .safe .stage-number {
            color: #10B981;
        }

        .warning .stage-number {
            color: #F59E0B;
        }

        .cooldown .stage-number {
            color: #F97316;
        }

        .danger .stage-number {
            color: #EF4444;
        }

        .stage-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .stage-description {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            line-height: 1.7;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .stage-quote {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-left: 3px solid;
            padding: 15px 18px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .safe .stage-quote {
            border-left-color: #10B981;
        }

        .warning .stage-quote {
            border-left-color: #F59E0B;
        }

        .cooldown .stage-quote {
            border-left-color: #F97316;
        }

        .danger .stage-quote {
            border-left-color: #EF4444;
        }

        /* Recovery section */
        .recovery-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(94, 123, 246, 0.15) 0%, rgba(94, 123, 246, 0.05) 100%);
            border: 2px solid rgba(94, 123, 246, 0.3);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px 35px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .recovery-section::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(94, 123, 246, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
        }

        .recovery-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5E7BF6 0%, #4A63D8 100%);
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 36px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(94, 123, 246, 0.4);
        }

        .recovery-title {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .recovery-description {
            font-size: 17px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            line-height: 1.7;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .stage-card {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
        }

        .stage-card:nth-child(1) {
            animation-delay: 0.1s;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .stage-card:nth-child(2) {
            animation-delay: 0.2s;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .stage-card:nth-child(3) {
            animation-delay: 0.3s;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .stage-card:nth-child(4) {
            animation-delay: 0.4s;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .recovery-section {
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease forwards;
            animation-delay: 0.5s;
            opacity: 0;
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .accountability-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            }

            .stage-card:nth-child(1),
            .stage-card:nth-child(2),
            .stage-card:nth-child(3),
            .stage-card:nth-child(4) {
                grid-column: auto;
            }

            .recovery-section {
                grid-column: 1 / 3;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .accountability-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 20px;
            }

            .stage-card:nth-child(1),
            .stage-card:nth-child(2),
            .stage-card:nth-child(3),
            .stage-card:nth-child(4) {
                grid-column: auto;
            }

            .recovery-section {
                grid-column: auto;
            }

            .stage-card {
                padding: 30px 24px;
            }

            .stage-title {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .recovery-section {
                padding: 35px 25px;
            }

            .recovery-title {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="accountability-container">
        
        <!-- Grid Layout -->
        <div class="accountability-grid">
            
            <!-- Stage 1: Safe -->
            <div class="stage-card safe">
                <div class="stage-number">Grace Period</div>
                <div class="stage-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i></div>
                <h3 class="stage-title">1 "Oops" Per Week</h3>
                <p class="stage-description">Miss once and your streak stays protected. We get it—life happens. You have breathing room.</p>
                <div class="stage-quote">"Your profile health stays strong. Keep going."</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 2: Warning -->
            <div class="stage-card warning">
                <div class="stage-number">Week 2 Below 50%</div>
                <div class="stage-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation"></i></div>
                <h3 class="stage-title">Warning Issued</h3>
                <p class="stage-description">You're at risk of downgrade. Hit your targets next week to stay at your current level.</p>
                <div class="stage-quote">"You're at risk. Hit your targets next week to stay in your tier."</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 3: Cooldown -->
            <div class="stage-card cooldown">
                <div class="stage-number">Week 3 Below 50%</div>
                <div class="stage-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-pause"></i></div>
                <h3 class="stage-title">Rewards Paused</h3>
                <p class="stage-description">Your premium rewards are temporarily suspended. Prove yourself this week to restore access.</p>
                <div class="stage-quote">"Prove yourself this week to restore access."</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Stage 4: Downgrade -->
            <div class="stage-card danger">
                <div class="stage-number">Week 4 Below 50%</div>
                <div class="stage-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down-long"></i></div>
                <h3 class="stage-title">Forced Downgrade</h3>
                <p class="stage-description">You drop from Advanced to Pro, or Pro to Starter. Your rewards adjust accordingly. Time to rebuild.</p>
                <div class="stage-quote">"Automatic downgrade. You'll need to earn your way back up."</div>
            </div>

            <!-- Recovery Section (spans 2 columns) -->
            <div class="recovery-section">
                <div class="recovery-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i></div>
                <h3 class="recovery-title">But Here's the Good News</h3>
                <p class="recovery-description">Hit <strong>100% for 4 weeks straight</strong> and you can upgrade again. Your progress resets, but you're back in the game with access to higher rewards. Consistency wins.</p>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</body>
</html>
